title: Silver 3 player looking for a Bronze/Silver team
body:
Think it'd be cool to join a small bronze/silver team to compete in bronze tournaments.
If you would like to invite me to your team it's perfectly fine.
Or if you'd like for me to start up a team and for you to join that's cool too.

Add my discord if interested JSV#0001

replies.body: sort of interested, sent u my link
